These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia, tulip, iris, poppy
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, green, emerald, blue, coral
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, october, may, march, june
There are 5 different nationalities: british, indonesian, nigerian, spanish, turkish
 1. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the indonesian##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the turkish is in an even position##4
 9. the british is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes emerald##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
12. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
13. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the indonesian##1
14. the turkish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
15. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who growsiris##1
16. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Flower      | tulip    | dahlia   | iris     | poppy      | zinnia      |
| Color           | emerald | coral | aquamarine    | blue | green |
| Birthday   | may       | november         | march      | october      | june    |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | spanish         | indonesian | turkish  | british   |

