.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
5 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, go, mah-jongg, bridge
There 5 different types of food: tomato, asparagus, cauliflower, apricot, strawberry
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, rabbit, rat, turtle
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, davidoff, alhambra, fonseca, pall-mall
 1. the person playing go is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 3. the person playing go is the person eating strawberry##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 8. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing go and the havana-smoker##2
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
11. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
13. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
14. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Game         | mah-jongg | scrabble | go   | canasta | bridge |
| Food   | cauliflower      | asparagus   | strawberry    | tomato        | apricot        |
| Pet           | rat         | turtle  | goldfish  | hedgehog   | rabbit      |
| Cigar     | havana        | fonseca  | alhambra | pall-mall | davidoff         |

