.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, chef, entrepreneur, writer, mechanic
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, family, horror, martial-arts, western
City: paris, edinburgh, prague, berlin, new-york
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, swisher, chaman, cain, montecristo
 1. the chef is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the writer is the writer##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is the chaman-smoker##1
10. the videographer is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the cain-smoker is the mechanic##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the swisher-smoker and the person watching action movies##2
13. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the videographer##3
14. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
15. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
16. the chef is on the left or right of the writer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
| Job      | mechanic       | videographer   | chef    | writer     | entrepreneur |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | family   | horror   | martial-arts | western       |
| City         | new-york | edinburgh | paris | berlin     | prague        |
| Cigar     | cain       | oliveros     | swisher  | chaman   | montecristo         |

