.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, cola, fanta, coffee
There are 5 different nationalities: turkish, indian, french, pakistani, canadian
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, folk, r&b, salsa, soul
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, february, april, november, december
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the french and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 2. the pakistani is on the far right##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
 5. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the turkish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 9. the person drinking coffee is the fan of soul##1
10. the indian is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the turkish##1
14. the person drinking 7up is the person drinking 7up##1
15. the person who's birthday is in november is the canadian##1
16. the person drinking cola is on the right of the french##1
17. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |     5      |
| Beverage          | 7up   | fanta   | lemonade | cola       | coffee       |
| Nationality   | indian | canadian     | french   | turkish     | pakistani    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | folk       | r&b    | electronic | soul       |
| Birthday     | december    | november | april   | february  | march |

