 4. the egyptian is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 8. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to hamburg and the photographer##2
 9. the electrician is on the left or right of the british##3
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the scientist is the french##1
12. the journalist is on the right of the photographer##1
13. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who growsorchid##1
14. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the photographer##1
15. the manager is on the right of the french##1
16. the person traveling to hamburg is the argentine##1

