5 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, goat, snake, cat
There are 5 different favourite colors: turquise, azure, coral, blood-red, grey
 1. the person who likes azure is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
 3. the accountant is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 4. the mechanic is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the security-guard is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 6. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 9. the accountant is the person who likes coral##1
10. the paramedic is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
11. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
13. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
14. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
15. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
16. the accountant is in an odd position##4
17. the owner of the snake is the person who likes coral##1
18. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
