5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dannemann, bluemaster, game, oliveros
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican, chinese, colombian, russian
 1. the person eating orange is the colombian##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 4. the person eating blueberry is in an even position##4
 5. the nigerian is on the far left##1
 6. the dannemann-smoker is between the russian and the oliveros-smoker##2
 7. the chinese is between the colombian and the game-smoker##2
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the person eating asparagus is the nigerian##1
10. the person eating apple is in the middle##1
11. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the nigerian is on the left of the game-smoker##1
13. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
14. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the nigerian##1
15. the game-smoker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
16. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |       3       |     4      |     5      |
