 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the motorbike and the person who growsazalea##2
 4. the person driving the roller is the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the entrepreneur is the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the librarian##1
 7. the designer is in the middle##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 9. the musician is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the dressmaker##1
13. the musician is the person who growsdaisy##1
14. the person drinking fanta is the person who growspoppy##1
