.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-15::.
5 different games are played: whist, chess, bridge, billiard, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, june, december, october, july
House: wooden, gothic-revival, futuristic, cottage, cape-cod
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, sailing, skateboarding
 1. the person playing chess is on the right of the wooden house##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 3. the wooden house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 4. the futuristic house is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 8. the gothic-revival house is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
11. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
13. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Game          | mah-jongg      | bridge       | whist | chess | billiard |
| Birthday   | december       | july    | october  | june  | may |
| House           | cape-cod         | gothic-revival | wooden      | futuristic     | cottage    |
| Sport         | skateboarding | baseball   | cricket   | sailing  | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-16::.
House: cape-cod, craftsman, farmhouse, modern, ranch-style
5 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, guinea-pig, pony, turtle
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, coffee, cola, milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire, sports, action, mystery
 1. the person watching action movies is the craftsman house##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 6. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
 7. the modern house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the owner of the fish##1
 9. the person watching action movies is the person drinking milk##1
10. the owner of the pony is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
13. the craftsman house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
14. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
15. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
16. the owner of the ferret is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |         2          |     3      |       4        |      5       |
| House         | craftsman     | ranch-style | farmhouse | modern | cape-cod      |
| Pet         | turtle     | pony               | fish       | guinea-pig     | ferret       |
| Beverage       | milk | hot-chocolate              | cola    | juice        | coffee |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | fantasy               | sports | mystery            | satire          |

