.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, sailing, baseball, skateboarding, water-polo
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, daffodil, aconite, daisy
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, carrot, strawberry, onion, lettuce
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, quad-bike, taxi, van
 1. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person driving the van and the person eating lettuce##2
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person eating lettuce and the person who growsdaisy##2
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
10. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
13. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person driving the taxi##1
15. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |      5      |
| Sport    | rugby       | baseball       | water-polo  | sailing | skateboarding     |
| Flower       | dahlia | daffodil    | aconite | balloon-flower  | daisy |
| Food         | onion     | nectarine | lettuce     | strawberry   | carrot    |
| Transport   | van         | motorbike  | quad-bike | airplane | taxi        |

