.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher, game, fonseca, alhambra
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, daffodil, bellflower, tulip
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, egyptian, mexican, pakistani
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketballing, tennis, cricket, basketball, soccer
 1. the swisher-smoker is the pakistani##1
 2. the game-smoker is on the left of the dutch##1
 3. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 6. the mexican is in an even position##4
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the egyptian is the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person who's sport is basketballing is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person who's sport is basketballing is on the right of the pakistani##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the game-smoker##1
13. the fonseca-smoker is in the middle##1
14. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
15. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Cigar         | swisher | alhambra | fonseca    | game     | vegafina   |
| Flower   | tulip     | poppy       | bellflower     | daffodil    | balloon-flower     |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | mexican   | argentine  | egyptian  | dutch     |
| Sport     | soccer      | basketballing  | basketball | cricket | tennis |

