.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, 7up, milk, almond-milk
5 different games are played: snooker, chess, monopoly, billiard, domino
The people have 5 different jobs:  musician, mechanic, scientist, lawyer, accountant
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, scooter, subway
 1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking 7up is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 7. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
 8. the musician is on the left of the scientist##1
 9. the person drinking milk is the lawyer##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
11. the musician is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
12. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing domino##1
13. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
14. the accountant is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |     4      |     5      |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | 7up | milk | almond-milk    | cola     |
| Game   | domino      | monopoly   | snooker     | billiard      | chess       |
| Job   | mechanic | accountant     | lawyer     | musician | scientist    |
| Transport     | subway   | roller   | motorbike   | scooter    | helicopter |

