.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, water, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade
City: liverpool, hannover, prague, hamburg, paris
The people have 5 different jobs:  photographer, manager, engineer, police-officer, dressmaker
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, boat, snowmobile, train, trike
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the police-officer##1
 2. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the engineer##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 7. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
 8. the engineer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 9. the manager is the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the police-officer is the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
12. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the train##1
13. the person driving the train is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
14. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
15. the photographer is the person driving the bike##1
16. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |       5       |
| Beverage         | water | coffee | lemonade    | milk      | almond-milk |
| City   | paris     | liverpool   | hannover     | hamburg | prague    |
| Job   | photographer  | manager  | dressmaker     | engineer       | police-officer     |
| Transport     | bike       | trike     | snowmobile | train       | boat          |

 